id: 260
event: agent
data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"Built the concept in `index.html` with local assets and a traceable `brand-spec.md`. It uses Babylon’s cream/wine/gold palette, arched hospitality imagery, preserved booking/function/tour/voucher/contact paths, and a multi-page-style structure inside one polished prototype entry.\n\n<artifact identifier=\"babylon-brisbane-restaurant\" type=\"text/html\" title=\"Babylon Brisbane Restaurant Concept\">\n<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>Babylon Brisbane · Riverside Middle Eastern Restaurant</title>\n  <style>\n    :root {\n      --bg:      oklch(98% 0.025 78);\n      --surface: oklch(100% 0.01 78);\n      --fg:      oklch(28% 0.07 14);\n      --muted:   oklch(45% 0.045 18);\n      --border:  oklch(89% 0.025 78);\n      --accent:  oklch(86% 0.105 88);\n\n      --accent-soft: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent) 18%, transparent);\n      --fg-soft:     color-mix(in oklch, var(--fg) 7%, transparent);\n      --wine-mid:    color-mix(in oklch, var(--fg) 86%, var(--surface));\n\n      --font-display: mendl-sans-dawn, 'Iowan Old Style', 'Charter', Georgia, serif;\n      --font-body:    transat, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;\n      --font-mono:    ui-monospace, 'JetBrains Mono', 'SF Mono', Menlo, monospace;\n\n      --fs-h1: clamp(48px, 8vw, 112px);\n      --fs-h2: clamp(32px, 5vw, 66px);\n      --fs-h3: 25px;\n      --fs-lead: 20px;\n      --fs-body: 17px;\n      --fs-meta: 12px;\n\n      --gap-md: 20px;\n      --gap-lg: 32px;\n      --gap-xl: 56px;\n      --gap-2xl: 96px;\n      --container: 1180px;\n      --gutter: 30px;\n      --radius: 4px;\n      --radius-lg: 18px;\n    }\n\n    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }\n    html { -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; scroll-behavior: smooth; }\n    body {\n      margin: 0;\n      background: var(--bg);\n      color: var(--fg);\n      font-family: var(--font-body);\n      font-size: var(--fs-body);\n      line-height: 1.55;\n      text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;\n      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\n    }\n    img, svg { display: block; max-width: 100%; }\n    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }\n    p { text-wrap: pretty; }\n    h1, h2, h3, h4 { text-wrap: balance; }\n\n    .container { max-width: var(--container); margin-inline: auto; padding-inline: var(--gutter); }\n    .section { padding-block: clamp(58px, 8vw, var(--gap-2xl)); }\n    .section + .section { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }\n    .stack { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }\n    .stack > * + * { margin-top: var(--gap-md); }\n    .row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--gap-md); }\n    .row-between { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: var(--gap-md); }\n    .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: var(--gap-lg); }\n    .grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: var(--gap-lg); }\n    .grid-2-1 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: var(--gap-xl); align-items: start; }\n    .grid-1-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr; gap: var(--gap-xl); align-items: start; }\n\n    h1 {\n      font-family: var(--font-display);\n      font-size: var(--fs-h1);\n      line-height: 0.92;\n      letter-spacing: 0.01em;\n      margin: 0;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      font-weight: 200;\n    }\n    h2 {\n      font-family: var(--font-display);\n      font-size: var(--fs-h2);\n      line-height: 0.98;\n      letter-spacing: 0.01em;\n      margin: 0;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      font-weight: 200;\n    }\n    h3 {\n      font-family: var(--font-display);\n      font-size: var(--fs-h3);\n      font-weight: 200;\n      line-height: 1.12;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      letter-spacing: 0.02em;\n      margin: 0;\n    }\n    .lead { font-size: var(--fs-lead); line-height: 1.55; color: var(--muted); max-width: 58ch; margin: 0; }\n    .eyebrow {\n      font-family: var(--font-mono);\n      font-size: 11px;\n      letter-spacing: 0.12em;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      color: var(--accent);\n      margin: 0 0 var(--gap-md);\n    }\n    .meta { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--fs-meta); color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.03em; }\n    .num { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }\n\n    .topnav {\n      position: sticky;\n      top: 0;\n      z-index: 10;\n      background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--bg) 93%, transparent);\n      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n    }\n    .topnav-inner { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; min-height: 76px; }\n    .topnav .logo img { width: 180px; height: auto; }\n    .topnav nav { display: flex; gap: 26px; align-items: center; }\n    .topnav nav a { font-size: 13px; color: var(--fg); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.07em; }\n    .topnav nav a:hover { color: var(--muted); }\n    .topnav .nav-cta { border: 1px solid var(--fg); padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: var(--radius); }\n\n    .btn {\n      display: inline-flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      gap: 8px;\n      min-height: 46px;\n      padding: 12px 22px;\n      border-radius: var(--radius);\n      border: 1px solid transparent;\n      font-size: 13px;\n      font-weight: 500;\n      letter-spacing: 0.08em;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      transition: transform 0.05s ease, background 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease, color 0.15s ease;\n    }\n    .btn:active { transform: translateY(1px); }\n    .btn-primary { background: var(--accent); color: var(--fg); border-color: var(--accent); }\n    .btn-primary:hover { background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent) 84%, var(--surface)); }\n    .btn-secondary { background: transparent; color: var(--fg); border-color: var(--fg); }\n    .btn-secondary:hover { background: var(--fg); color: var(--surface); }\n    .btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: var(--fg); border-color: transparent; padding-inline: 8px; }\n    .btn-ghost:hover { color: var(--muted); }\n    .btn-arrow::after { content: '→'; transition: transform 0.15s ease; }\n    .btn-arrow:hover::after { transform: translateX(2px); }\n\n    .hero-full {\n      position: relative;\n      min-height: calc(100vh - 76px);\n      display: grid;\n      align-items: end;\n      overflow: hidden;\n      background: var(--fg);\n      color: var(--surface);\n    }\n    .hero-full::before {\n      content: '';\n      position: absolute;\n      inset: 0;\n      background:\n        linear-gradient(to bottom, color-mix(in oklch, var(--fg) 18%, transparent), color-mix(in oklch, var(--fg) 88%, transparent)),\n        url('assets/fire.webp') center / cover;\n      opacity: 0.82;\n    }\n    .hero-full .container { position: relative; width: 100%; padding-block: clamp(70px, 10vw, 130px); }\n    .hero-logo-mark { width: min(430px, 82vw); margin-bottom: 34px; }\n    .hero-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.18fr 0.82fr; gap: var(--gap-xl); align-items: end; }\n    .hero-full .lead { color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 78%, var(--accent)); }\n    .hero-cta { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 30px; }\n    .hero-panel {\n      border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 28%, transparent);\n      background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--fg) 62%, transparent);\n      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n      border-radius: 50% 50% 0 0;\n      padding: 58px 30px 30px;\n    }\n    .hero-panel .meta { color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 75%, transparent); }\n\n    .choice-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); border-top: 1px solid var(--fg); border-left: 1px solid var(--fg); }\n    .choice {\n      min-height: 170px;\n      padding: 22px;\n      border-right: 1px solid var(--fg);\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--fg);\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      justify-content: space-between;\n      transition: background 0.15s ease, color 0.15s ease;\n    }\n    .choice:hover { background: var(--fg); color: var(--surface); }\n    .choice span { color: currentColor; opacity: 0.72; }\n\n    .arched-img {\n      position: relative;\n      overflow: hidden;\n      border-radius: 50% 50% 0 0;\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      min-height: 390px;\n      background: var(--fg-soft);\n    }\n    .arched-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; min-height: inherit; }\n    .venue-card { display: grid; grid-template-rows: minmax(260px, 1fr) auto; gap: 22px; }\n    .venue-card p { margin: 10px 0 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 15px; }\n    .venue-card .btn { margin-top: 18px; }\n\n    .wine-band { background: var(--fg); color: var(--surface); }\n    .wine-band .lead,\n    .wine-band .meta,\n    .wine-band .quote-author { color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 72%, var(--accent)); }\n    .wine-band .section + .section { border-top-color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 20%, transparent); }\n    .wine-band .btn-secondary { color: var(--surface); border-color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 46%, transparent); }\n    .wine-band .btn-secondary:hover { background: var(--surface); color: var(--fg); }\n    .wine-band .log-row { border-top-color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 24%, transparent); }\n\n    .log-row {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: 150px minmax(0, 1fr) 120px;\n      gap: var(--gap-lg);\n      align-items: baseline;\n      padding: 22px 0;\n      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);\n    }\n    .pull { text-align: right; }\n    .quote {\n      font-family: var(--font-display);\n      font-size: clamp(28px, 3.2vw, 44px);\n      line-height: 1.08;\n      letter-spacing: 0.01em;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      max-width: 24ch;\n    }\n    .quote-author { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; margin-top: var(--gap-md); }\n    .quote-mark { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 140px; line-height: 0.7; color: var(--accent); opacity: 0.35; margin-bottom: -28px; }\n\n    .mini-pages { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 0.85fr 1.15fr; gap: var(--gap-xl); align-items: start; }\n    .page-list { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }\n    .page-link {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: 54px 1fr auto;\n      gap: 18px;\n      align-items: center;\n      padding: 20px 0;\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n    }\n    .page-link:hover h3 { color: var(--muted); }\n    .hours-card { border: 1px solid var(--fg); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 26px; }\n    .hours-card dl { margin: 0; display: grid; gap: 14px; }\n    .hours-card div { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 12px; }\n    .hours-card div:last-child { border-bottom: 0; padding-bottom: 0; }\n    .hours-card dt { color: var(--muted); }\n    .hours-card dd { margin: 0; text-align: right; }\n    .pagefoot { padding-block: var(--gap-xl); color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }\n    .pagefoot .row-between { flex-wrap: wrap; gap: var(--gap-md); }\n\n    @media (max-width: 1040px) {\n      .choice-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }\n      .hero-grid, .mini-pages { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n      .hero-panel { border-radius: var(--radius-lg); max-width: 560px; }\n      .topnav nav { display: none; }\n    }\n    @media (max-width: 920px) {\n      .grid-2, .grid-3, .grid-2-1, .grid-1-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n      .log-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 8px; }\n      .pull { text-align: left; }\n      .choice-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n      .page-link { grid-template-columns: 42px 1fr; }\n      .page-link .btn { grid-column: 2; justify-self: start; }\n      .hours-card div { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n      .hours-card dd { text-align: left; }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <header class=\"topnav\" id=\"top\">\n    <div class=\"container topnav-inner\">\n      <a class=\"logo\" href=\"#top\" aria-label=\"Babylon Brisbane home\">\n        <img src=\"assets/logo.png\" alt=\"Babylon Brisbane\" />\n      </a>\n      <nav aria-label=\"Primary navigation\">\n        <a href=\"#eat-drink\">Eat &amp; Drink</a>\n        <a href=\"#whats-on\">What’s On</a>\n        <a href=\"#functions\">Functions</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        <a class=\"nav-cta\" href=\"https://www.sevenrooms.com/explore/babylonbrisbane/reservations/create/search?tracking=babylon-brisbane-widget&amp;venues=babylonbrisbane%2Cfridaysbrisbane%2Cregattahotel%2Ctheboatshed%2Cdeathandcobris%2Ctheboundaryhotelaus%2Cportoffice%2Cjimmysonthemall%2Cpignwhistleriverside%2Criverlandbrisbane\">Book a table</a>\n      </nav>\n    </div>\n  </header>\n\n  <main id=\"content\">\n    <section class=\"hero-full\" data-od-id=\"home\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"hero-grid\">\n          <div>\n            <img class=\"hero-logo-mark\" src=\"assets/hero-logo.png\" alt=\"Babylon Brisbane\" />\n            <p class=\"eyebrow\">Eagle Street Pier · Brisbane River</p>\n            <h1>A Taste of the Middle East in Brisbane</h1>\n            <p class=\"lead\" style=\"margin-top: 24px;\">On the banks of the Brisbane River, Babylon Brisbane blends ancient Levant inspiration with modern dining across restaurants, bars, terraces and vibrant function spaces.</p>\n            <div class=\"hero-cta\">\n              <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://www.sevenrooms.com/explore/babylonbrisbane/reservations/create/search?tracking=babylon-brisbane-widget&amp;venues=babylonbrisbane%2Cfridaysbrisbane%2Cregattahotel%2Ctheboatshed%2Cdeathandcobris%2Ctheboundaryhotelaus%2Cportoffice%2Cjimmysonthemall%2Cpignwhistleriverside%2Criverlandbrisbane\">Book a table</a>\n              <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"#eat-drink\">View the menu</a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <aside class=\"hero-panel\">\n            <p class=\"meta\">Restaurant Hours</p>\n            <h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0 18px;\">Sunday–Thursday 11:30am–9:00pm<br />Friday–Saturday 11:30am–10:00pm</h3>\n            <p class=\"meta\">Babylon Gardens stays open until 12:30am Friday and Saturday.</p>\n          </aside>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"quick-actions\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"choice-grid\">\n          <a class=\"choice\" href=\"https://www.sevenrooms.com/explore/babylonbrisbane/reservations/create/search?tracking=babylon-brisbane-widget&amp;venues=babylonbrisbane%2Cfridaysbrisbane%2Cregattahotel%2Ctheboatshed%2Cdeathandcobris%2Ctheboundaryhotelaus%2Cportoffice%2Cjimmysonthemall%2Cpignwhistleriverside%2Criverlandbrisbane\">\n            <span class=\"meta\">01</span>\n            <h3>Book a table</h3>\n          </a>\n          <a class=\"choice\" href=\"#eat-drink\">\n            <span class=\"meta\">02</span>\n            <h3>View the menu</h3>\n          </a>\n          <a class=\"choice\" href=\"#functions\">\n            <span class=\"meta\">03</span>\n            <h3>Host a function</h3>\n          </a>\n          <a class=\"choice\" href=\"https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=1rxMmuuhByW\">\n            <span class=\"meta\">04</span>\n            <h3>Take a 3D tour</h3>\n          </a>\n          <a class=\"choice\" href=\"https://thepassapp.com.au/the-pass-gift-cards/\">\n            <span class=\"meta\">05</span>\n            <h3>Gift vouchers</h3>\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"intro\">\n      <div class=\"container grid-2-1\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Riverside dining · Levant inspiration</p>\n          <h2>Cascading down three levels, made for long lunches and late nights.</h2>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"stack\">\n          <p class=\"lead\">From bold Middle Eastern flavours and generous share plates to riverside cocktails and terrace dining, Babylon invites guests to settle in and stay awhile.</p>\n          <p style=\"margin: 0; color: var(--muted);\">The concept keeps the existing page intent but makes the journey clearer: choose your experience first, then move naturally into menus, events, functions and contact.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"eat-drink\" id=\"eat-drink\">\n      <div class=\"container stack\" style=\"gap: 56px;\">\n        <div class=\"row-between\">\n          <div style=\"max-width: 44ch;\">\n            <p class=\"eyebrow\">Eat &amp; Drink</p>\n            <h2>Restaurant, gardens, terrace — one riverside address.</h2>\n          </div>\n          <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"https://babylonbrisbane.com.au/eat-drink/\">Open current menu</a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"grid-3\">\n          <article class=\"venue-card\">\n            <div class=\"arched-img\"><img src=\"assets/restaurant.webp\" alt=\"Babylon restaurant dining room and food\" /></div>\n            <div>\n              <h3>The Restaurant</h3>\n              <p>Inspired by the rich culinary heritage of the Levant, the menu celebrates bold spices, wood-fired meats, generous shared plates, fire-kissed seafood and house-made baklava.</p>\n              <a class=\"btn btn-ghost btn-arrow\" href=\"https://babylonbrisbane.com.au/the-restaurant/\">Read more</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"venue-card\">\n            <div class=\"arched-img\"><img src=\"assets/gardens.webp\" alt=\"Babylon Gardens terrace with drinks\" /></div>\n            <div>\n              <h3>Babylon Gardens</h3>\n              <p>A lush, two-tiered bar and terrace with panoramic views, East Mediterranean-inspired bites, curated wine and signature cocktails with a breeze off the river.</p>\n              <a class=\"btn btn-ghost btn-arrow\" href=\"https://babylonbrisbane.com.au/babylon-gardens/\">Read more</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"venue-card\">\n            <div class=\"arched-img\"><img src=\"assets/functions.jpg\" alt=\"Private event table setting at Babylon Brisbane\" /></div>\n            <div>\n              <h3>Private Events</h3>\n              <p>Versatile spaces for corporate events, milestone celebrations and intimate gatherings, with tailored food, drinks packages and dedicated event support.</p>\n              <a class=\"btn btn-ghost btn-arrow\" href=\"#functions\">Plan a function</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"wine-band\">\n      <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"whats-on\" id=\"whats-on\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n          <div class=\"row-between\" style=\"margin-bottom: 36px;\">\n            <div>\n              <p class=\"eyebrow\">What’s On</p>\n              <h2>Events worth booking around.</h2>\n            </div>\n            <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"https://babylonbrisbane.com.au/whats-on/\">View all</a>\n          </div>\n          <div>\n            <article class=\"log-row\">\n              <span class=\"meta\">May 2026</span>\n              <div>\n                <h3>Mother’s Day</h3>\n                <p style=\"margin: 4px 0 0; color: inherit; opacity: 0.76; font-size: 14px;\">A polished event tile for the seasonal booking moment already visible on the live site.</p>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"pull meta\">Dining</span>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"log-row\">\n              <span class=\"meta\">This May</span>\n              <div>\n                <h3>Win big this May with a prize valued up to $7k</h3>\n                <p style=\"margin: 4px 0 0; color: inherit; opacity: 0.76; font-size: 14px;\">The Pass app promotion preserved as a high-priority campaign entry.</p>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"pull meta\">The Pass</span>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"log-row\">\n              <span class=\"meta\">Weekly</span>\n              <div>\n                <h3>Live Music · Meze &amp; Mimosa · Ottoman’s Lunch</h3>\n                <p style=\"margin: 4px 0 0; color: inherit; opacity: 0.76; font-size: 14px;\">Recurring moments grouped so the page feels curated instead of carousel-heavy.</p>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"pull meta\">Riverside</span>\n            </article>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"quote\">\n        <div class=\"container grid-1-2\">\n          <div class=\"arched-img\" style=\"min-height: 520px;\"><img src=\"assets/meze.webp\" alt=\"Middle Eastern share plates at Babylon Brisbane\" /></div>\n          <div style=\"align-self: center;\">\n            <div class=\"quote-mark\">\"</div>\n            <blockquote class=\"quote\">Bold Middle Eastern flavours and generous share plates, served with genuine warmth and care.</blockquote>\n            <p class=\"quote-author\">Babylon Brisbane menu story</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"functions\" id=\"functions\">\n      <div class=\"container mini-pages\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Functions</p>\n          <h2>Spaces designed to impress, from private dining to sprawling terraces.</h2>\n          <p class=\"lead\" style=\"margin-top: 22px;\">Whether it’s a corporate event, milestone celebration or intimate gathering, the concept gives the function path its own clear landing moment.</p>\n          <div class=\"hero-cta\">\n            <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://babylonbrisbane.com.au/functions/\">Function enquiry</a>\n            <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"https://babylonbrisbane.com.au/functions/\">Current functions page</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"page-list\">\n          <a class=\"page-link\" href=\"https://babylonbrisbane.com.au/the-restaurant/\">\n            <span class=\"num meta\">01</span>\n            <div><h3>The Restaurant</h3><p style=\"margin: 4px 0 0; color: var(--muted);\">Charcoal grills, open flames and slow-cooked dishes for seated dining.</p></div>\n            <span class=\"btn btn-ghost btn-arrow\">Open</span>\n          </a>\n          <a class=\"page-link\" href=\"https://babylonbrisbane.com.au/babylon-gardens/\">\n            <span class=\"num meta\">02</span>\n            <div><h3>Babylon Gardens</h3><p style=\"margin: 4px 0 0; color: var(--muted);\">Two-tiered alfresco terrace with space for up to 500 guests.</p></div>\n            <span class=\"btn btn-ghost btn-arrow\">Open</span>\n          </a>\n          <a class=\"page-link\" href=\"https://babylonbrisbane.com.au/functions/\">\n            <span class=\"num meta\">03</span>\n            <div><h3>Private Events &amp; Functions</h3><p style=\"margin: 4px 0 0; color: var(--muted);\">Tailored drinks packages, event food and dedicated support.</p></div>\n            <span class=\"btn btn-ghost btn-arrow\">Open</span>\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"contact\" id=\"contact\">\n      <div class=\"container grid-2\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Come in and say hello</p>\n          <h2>145 Eagle Street, Brisbane City, 4000</h2>\n          <p class=\"lead\" style=\"margin-top: 20px;\">For bookings, functions or general enquiries, keep the existing direct paths visible instead of burying them in a footer.</p>\n          <div class=\"hero-cta\">\n            <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"tel:+61731866655\">(07) 3186 6655</a>\n            <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"mailto:info@babylonbrisbane.com.au\">Email us</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <aside class=\"hours-card\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Opening hours</p>\n          <dl>\n            <div><dt>Restaurant · Sunday–Thursday</dt><dd>11:30am–9:00pm</dd></div>\n            <div><dt>Restaurant · Friday–Saturday</dt><dd>11:30am–10:00pm</dd></div>\n            <div><dt>Gardens · Sunday–Monday</dt><dd>11:00am–10:00pm</dd></div>\n            <div><dt>Gardens · Tuesday–Thursday</dt><dd>11:00am–11:00pm</dd></div>\n            <div><dt>Gardens · Friday–Saturday</dt><dd>11:00am–12:30am</dd></div>\n          </dl>\n        </aside>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"cta-strip\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n      <div class=\"container\" style=\"max-width: 680px;\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">The Pass app</p>\n        <h2>Get $10 off your first order.</h2>\n        <p class=\"lead\" style=\"margin: 16px auto 32px;\">Download The Pass app and earn points and perks with every order at 200+ pubs, bars and restaurants Australia-wide.</p>\n        <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://links.thepassapp.com.au/mwsQzm6WL2b\">Download the app</a>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n  </main>\n\n  <footer class=\"pagefoot\">\n    <div class=\"container row-between\">\n      <div>\n        <strong style=\"color: var(--fg);\">Babylon Brisbane</strong><br />\n        <span>Middle Eastern restaurant and riverside bar · 145 Eagle Street, Brisbane City</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"row\" style=\"flex-wrap: wrap;\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BabylonBrisbane/\">Facebook</a>\n        <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/babylonbrisbane/\">Instagram</a>\n        <a href=\"https://babylonbrisbane.com.au/faqs/\">FAQs</a>\n        <a href=\"https://thepassapp.com.au/the-pass-gift-cards/\">Gift Vouchers</a>\n        <a href=\"#top\">Return to top</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n</artifact>"}

